title: A Review of Episode 1219 Bill Burr
description:
Bill Burr is one of the greatest standup comedians of all time. He’s such a fantastic guest to have on Joe’s podcast and always a pleasure to listen to. He has a show on Netflix called F is for family and a brilliant one man podcast.

Enjoy my review folks!
